These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, italian, japanese, thai, turkish
There are 7 different favourite colors: apricot, coral, red, brown, lavender, ebony, lilac
 1. the australian is between the italian and the turkish##2
 2. the french is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the japanese is between the person who likes red and the person who likes lavender##2
 5. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person who likes coral is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes red##2
 8. the person who likes coral is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the thai##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the person who likes red##1
11. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | italian | australian | turkish | french    | indonesian | japanese   | thai    |
| Color         | ebony  | coral   | brown | apricot | red   | lilac | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, taxi, scooter, car, airplane, bike, helicopter
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the bike and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person driving the car is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Transport          | airplane | scooter | bike | taxi | helicopter | bus      | car  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

