.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german, indian, mexican, pakistani, polish
There are 7 different favourite colors: green, pink, yellow, blue, white, red, turquise
 1. the mexican is on the left of the canadian##1
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who likes white is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the indian is the person who likes blue##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 8. the person who likes green is between the person who likes turquise and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who likes red##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | canadian | dutch   | indian | german | pakistani |
| Color           | white | red     | pink     | yellow | blue   | green   | turquise    |

