.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
House: craftsman, tower, victorian, colonial, cottage, palace, townhouse
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the victorian house##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the cottage house##1
 3. the palace house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the cottage house##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the colonial house is between the person drinking juice and the palace house##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the colonial house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the tower house##1
10. the craftsman house is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| House   | cottage | colonial | palace | townhouse | craftsman | victorian | tower  |

