.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
The people have 7 different jobs:  entrepreneur, videographer, electrician, pilot, dancer, accountant, scientist
1. the pilot is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the dancer is the fan of disco##1
3. the entrepreneur is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the dancer##1
5. the entrepreneur is in the middle##1
6. the accountant is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the electrician is on the left of the dancer##1
8. the videographer is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Job     | videographer | accountant | scientist       | entrepreneur | electrician | dancer | pilot |

