.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, cycling, lacrosse, parkour, rowing, snowboarding
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking lemonade##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | lemonade | coffee | iced-tea | water | hot-chocolate     | almond-milk |
| Sport   | cycling   | lacrosse    | snowboarding    | parkour      | climbing  | badminton | rowing |

