.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, dog, turtle, fish, horse, goldfish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the dog is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the owner of the fish##2
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Pet   | hamster | goat    | turtle | dog   | horse | goldfish    | fish |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

