.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, mouse, ferret, rabbit, guinea-pig, lizard
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Pet   | goat | ferret     | guinea-pig | rabbit | mouse | lizard  | hedgehog |
| Transport     | quad-bike | skateboard | taxi   | bus     | trike    | motorbike | tram   |

