.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola, fanta, milk, mirinda, tea
City: prague, nizza, boston, paris, marseilles, edinburgh, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to nizza##2
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up       | tea         | milk         | fanta   | cola        | mirinda |
| City      | san-francisco | boston | prague | marseilles | nizza | edinburgh | paris  |

