.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, puzzles, reading, rock-climbing, singing, woodworking
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, subway, snowmobile, bike, jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
