3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person driving the bike and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing       | puzzles    | rock-climbing | reading | hiking     | cooking       |
| Transport   | taxi    | snowmobile | jet-ski | bike        | subway | scooter | boat |

